mixin showBanner(bannerName, bannerImage)
    .col-md-3.col-xs-3.about-grids
        img(src=`./dist/images/home/banner/${bannerImage}.jpg` alt="No Image")
        h5 #{bannerName}

h3.ila-title OVERVIEW
.about-ilainfo
    p
        | Currently, all of our reports are stored and built in different systems
        | although they have same purpose but in different view.
        | This report is a cosolidation to review our current reports which are mainly using,
        | their definition, purpose and finding the better solution for centralize all these
        | reports to same platform. Below are 4 main systems we are reviewing:
    
    +showBanner("CRM", "crm")
    +showBanner("ERP", "erp")
    +showBanner("Power BI", "bi")
    +showBanner("LMS Moodle", "lms")
    .clearfix  